{"tid":116522,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"扭蛋機俾完錢冇蛋出, 一星期後收到隻蛋","createTime":"2017-02-11T13:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T14:14:25.000Z","uid":43710,"like":26,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f25aa213e611a6ae39f6ec5801205a15f49d8fd","tid":116522,"uid":43710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的上個禮拜想扭隻寵物小精靈<br />\n點知嘟完八達通後先發覺扭蛋機冇晒蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pT643q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pT643q.jpg&h=4c0ee732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是即刻搵個熱線電話求助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  熱線小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔該我嘟左八達通俾佢扣左錢之後先發現部機無晒蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哦 我地會寄番隻蛋俾你 麻煩你講下你扭果隻係咩黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 寵物小精靈 坐係個杯度嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好嘅 麻煩你留低地址 我地會三個星期內寄番隻蛋俾你 如果無同款嘅我地會搵類似嘅俾你<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n今日終於收到 估下係咩黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾完屎開估<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5R4U7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5R4U7y.jpg&h=28344898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681aa20257bf84ac86bfd4e70468dfe4d093aa16","tid":116522,"uid":42735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:10:15.000Z","msg":"又多左隻手？"},{"pid":"01411afb6107ce28d2a2387bde3d8fbd6ada75b0","tid":116522,"uid":49257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c